Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.14,0:00:18.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Everyone, Kaleido Star is about to start.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.03,0:00:21.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}When you watch Kaleido Star, I want \Nyou to keep your room brightly lit,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.29,0:00:24.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and sit as far from the TV as you can.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.88,0:00:27.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Well, well, well. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.04,0:00:29.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Do you have something you \Nwant to be in the future?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.61,0:00:31.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A school teacher? A doctor?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.63,0:00:33.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You must have all kinds of \Ndreams of what you want to be.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.38,0:00:36.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Doing something you want \Nto do is very difficult.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.80,0:00:39.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But let's have a good attitude and \Nnever give up on what we want to do.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.72,0:00:41.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Let's! Let's!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.99,0:00:50.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The dream everyone is looking \Nfor must be someplace{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.02,0:00:52.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It has to be somewhere {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.53,0:01:00.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Until your dream comes true \Nsomeday, you're not alone{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.25,0:01:14.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Remember how I used to say \NI could make it to the end?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.55,0:01:20.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I must have been pretending to be tough{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.90,0:01:29.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Everything I did was reckless \Nand it never got me anywhere{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.56,0:01:36.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But you alone were always beside me{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.95,0:01:42.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The dream everyone is looking \Nfor must be somewhere{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.91,0:01:45.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You can start going forward {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.50,0:01:51.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}From this moment, something will start{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.13,0:01:53.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I want to believe that {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.17,0:02:00.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The light I haven't seen yet is \Nbeaming toward the promised place{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.68,0:02:10.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Until your dream comes true \Nsomeday, you're not alone{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.50,0:03:17.59,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"An Amazing Sinister Rumor."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.59,0:03:23.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And now, I present to you my home page!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.64,0:03:25.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, it's so cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.68,0:03:28.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But don't you think this picture \Nof Kaleido Stage is kinda skewed?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.77,0:03:29.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.81,0:03:32.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I already got permission from the Boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.14,0:03:33.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.52,0:03:37.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm planning on putting up everyone's \Npictures in the gallery.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.15,0:03:40.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In particular, Anna's pictures \Nhave special features.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.61,0:03:42.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When did you take these pictures?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.61,0:03:44.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When Anna flubs a gag,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.91,0:03:46.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that's the best time to take a picture.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.41,0:03:49.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, are you going to post \Neveryone's pictures?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.45,0:03:52.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well... That was my plan, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.37,0:03:53.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.37,0:03:56.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lately, someone quits every day. So...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.50,0:03:57.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.46,0:03:59.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you hear?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.09,0:04:02.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The other day, three people quit at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.55,0:04:08.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be very disappointed if someone quits \Nas soon as I post the picture on the website.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.60,0:04:09.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.43,0:04:13.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lately I'm concentrating my energies \Non writing original stories.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.69,0:04:15.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Original stories?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.35,0:04:16.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.19,0:04:20.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cute stories, scary stories, \Netcetera, etcetera.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.32,0:04:21.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How about something funny?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.53,0:04:23.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nope!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.15,0:04:25.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora, you have a guest.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.36,0:04:26.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.20,0:04:28.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She looks Japanese.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.74,0:04:31.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Japanese? I wonder who she could be.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.20,0:04:32.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She said she would wait for you in the lobby.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.71,0:04:34.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.54,0:04:37.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if she was in the \Nrhythmic gymnastics club.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.55,0:04:41.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.59,0:04:42.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.38,0:04:43.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.34,0:04:46.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're late.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.68,0:04:48.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got tired of waiting for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.76,0:04:50.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Manami...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.09,0:04:53.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Did I bother you by showing up here?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.56,0:04:57.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, no. Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.00,0:04:58.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad you came.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.81,0:05:01.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It isn't comfortable standing here,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.69,0:05:03.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so why don't we have a \Ncup of coffee somewhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.44,0:05:04.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.53,0:05:06.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You just need to be back here before \Nthe evening performance starts. Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.95,0:05:07.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.95,0:05:08.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.77,0:05:09.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.74,0:05:11.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should go change your clothes quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.66,0:05:14.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's right. Excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.29,0:05:20.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you come here, Manami?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.87,0:05:22.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was chosen as an exchange student,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.92,0:05:24.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and I'm going to stay in \NBoston for three months.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.59,0:05:25.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.59,0:05:27.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As usual, you're doing well at school.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.43,0:05:31.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course. I've been studying hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.81,0:05:34.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When it comes to studying, I stand \Nno chance against you, Manami.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.77,0:05:36.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, maybe it's because
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.14,0:05:38.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you were the only one going \Nto English Conversation School
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.06,0:05:40.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,while everybody else was in cram school.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.02,0:05:41.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't expect to keep \Nyour grades up doing that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.98,0:05:45.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah... That's what you'd \Ntell me all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.86,0:05:48.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I was a little surprised today.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.41,0:05:48.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.95,0:05:52.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I never expected you to play a lead role.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.91,0:05:55.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When you said that you'd be a Kaleido Star,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.58,0:05:58.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought it was ridiculous.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.11,0:05:59.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who ever thought that you'd really do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.67,0:06:02.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well... I'm not exactly at the \Npoint where you can call me a star.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.96,0:06:03.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This time,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.55,0:06:07.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just happened to be lucky enough \Nto co-star with Miss Layla, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.35,0:06:08.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, so that's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.81,0:06:16.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you have any regrets?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.10,0:06:17.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.85,0:06:23.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I don't have any regrets.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.52,0:06:27.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think I would have regretted it \Nmore if I'd just stayed in Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.69,0:06:28.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.66,0:06:31.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did something happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.16,0:06:32.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean, "something"?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.24,0:06:35.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I just wondered if you're having \Na hard time deciding what you should do.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.29,0:06:38.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,'Cause someone who's always \Nconfident like you...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.00,0:06:40.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you think that sounds rude?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.67,0:06:41.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.67,0:06:43.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're treating me like an idiot \Nwho has nothing to worry about.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.84,0:06:46.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... I never meant it like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.17,0:06:47.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, never mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.09,0:06:50.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's almost the time to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.13,0:06:53.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,During your evening performance, \NI will wait for you backstage.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.22,0:06:55.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Wait for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.18,0:06:56.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.06,0:06:58.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to stay in your room tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.56,0:06:59.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.24,0:07:00.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't make a hotel reservation.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.85,0:07:02.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh. Really...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.69,0:07:09.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is our backstage.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.74,0:07:14.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You and I can't even hold \Neach other in our arms!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.70,0:07:17.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care if you're a \Nghost or anything else.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.16,0:07:18.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please stay beside me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.95,0:07:20.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.37,0:07:21.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Sora...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.47,0:07:23.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well... Who is that...?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.17,0:07:25.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, she's my friend, Manami.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.21,0:07:26.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How do you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.38,0:07:27.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.09,0:07:31.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We were acting out a script \Nthat Mia put on her website.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.51,0:07:32.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You want to give it a try too, Sora?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.80,0:07:34.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.22,0:07:36.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For Sora, I think this role is perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.47,0:07:37.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which one?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.26,0:07:39.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A mysterious comical loco girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.39,0:07:40.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.48,0:07:41.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That sounds like a choice role.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.89,0:07:43.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's perfect! It's perfect!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.60,0:07:46.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the other hand, my lines \Nare embarrassing to read.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.11,0:07:48.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I think girls will love it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.53,0:07:49.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right? Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.69,0:08:29.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was a great show.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.53,0:08:30.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was great.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.94,0:08:32.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Sora.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.28,0:08:33.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ken...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.28,0:08:35.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is your body not feeling well?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.24,0:08:36.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Not really...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.49,0:08:38.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please tell me the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.53,0:08:40.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you overwork yourself too \Nmuch, you'll hurt yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.66,0:08:41.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.58,0:08:43.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've already noticed \Nit yourself, haven't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.91,0:08:46.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not as trained as Miss Layla.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.50,0:08:49.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you're doing the same performance \Nas her every single day.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.13,0:08:50.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you expect?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.50,0:08:52.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.63,0:08:56.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, do you mind if I give you support?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.05,0:08:57.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.05,0:08:58.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is, if you don't mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.76,0:09:01.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just in case, I already got \Npermission from the Boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.52,0:09:03.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What I'm going to do is \Ndesign your training menu,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.31,0:09:05.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,give you advice about what \Nto eat... that kind of stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.14,0:09:08.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In short, I'll be like a trainer.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.65,0:09:10.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it's not too much trouble for you...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.57,0:09:12.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How can it be trouble?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.82,0:09:15.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.24,0:09:19.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The reason why my body is hurting is because \Nit cannot keep up with my performance.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.62,0:09:21.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, did you hear?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.79,0:09:23.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Karen is also going to quit.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.33,0:09:25.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That rumor could really be true.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.96,0:09:28.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As I suspected, he's headhunting everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.58,0:09:31.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaleido Stage is, like, in trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.26,0:09:33.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.92,0:09:34.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.72,0:09:36.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The story you were just talking about...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.55,0:09:39.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think everyone's quitting because \Nthey don't like you playing the lead.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.76,0:09:40.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.55,0:09:43.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I were playing the leading role, \Nlike, everything would be much better.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.10,0:09:48.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Where is Manami?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.82,0:09:52.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When we got back, she wasn't here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.02,0:09:53.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.82,0:10:02.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, the rumor is that everyone is leaving \Nbecause I'm playing the leading role...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.99,0:10:03.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if it's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.54,0:10:06.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How could it be true? Are you kidding?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.20,0:10:10.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like you to take \Ntheir words seriously, Sora.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.43,0:10:11.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.38,0:10:14.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I also heard the rumor that there \Nwill be another theatrical company.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.84,0:10:16.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaleido Stage's rival?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.84,0:10:18.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, they're headhunting everybody?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.09,0:10:23.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not a big deal. 'Cause we have \NSora, Miss Layla and Mr. Yuri.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.43,0:10:26.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All these things she has to deal with...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.73,0:10:27.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.91,0:10:29.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Manami, you're still here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.52,0:10:30.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't want me to stay here?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.46,0:10:33.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... No... I didn't mean like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.32,0:10:37.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One, two... One, two...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.44,0:10:43.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One, two... One, two... One, two...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.33,0:10:45.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One, two...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.20,0:10:47.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good, good. You can do it slowly, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.54,0:10:48.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.46,0:10:52.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to work hard and build my muscles.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.39,0:10:55.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides muscles, you ended up with \Na boyfriend before I knew it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.55,0:10:57.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A boyfriend? Oh, you mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.01,0:10:59.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, Ken is not anything like that at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.34,0:11:00.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not at all...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.97,0:11:04.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've brought some protein juice.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.35,0:11:06.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you drink it one hour after you work out,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.68,0:11:08.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it will help your muscles to recover faster.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.20,0:11:10.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go get it for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.25,0:11:12.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Ken.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.81,0:11:14.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Was he crying?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.48,0:11:16.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.90,0:11:20.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Too many things happened today.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.46,0:11:22.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Manami, you want to take a bath, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.45,0:11:23.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.53,0:11:25.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.12,0:11:26.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, don't bother...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.40,0:11:27.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm doing this for crime prevention.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.87,0:11:29.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've not done anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.79,0:11:30.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've not done anything yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.93,0:11:34.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora, you haven't cut your \Nhair in a while, have you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.27,0:11:37.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah, come to think of it...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.20,0:11:41.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll cut your hair for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.30,0:11:44.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.59,0:11:47.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I used to be forced to play \Nhairdressers and customers.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.31,0:11:48.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was a customer and...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.19,0:11:50.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Forced?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.23,0:11:52.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, well... I didn't mean like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.06,0:11:54.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.02,0:12:01.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You belong at Kaleido Stage now, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.57,0:12:08.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been watching you all day long, Sora.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.64,0:12:11.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You pretend to be tough, acting \Nlike everything is cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.04,0:12:14.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I wonder if, in reality, you \Nmight be crying behind that look.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.33,0:12:16.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, you were concerned about me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.96,0:12:19.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not really...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.01,0:12:23.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To tell you the truth, I came \Nhere to see your regretful face.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.93,0:12:24.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.14,0:12:32.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.92,0:12:34.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.31,0:12:37.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything is going smoothly.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.55,0:13:08.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"After I see your show one more time,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.03,0:13:10.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll be taking an evening flight to Boston.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.36,0:13:11.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Manami."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.22,0:13:13.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Manami...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.59,0:13:18.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One, two... One, two...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.56,0:13:21.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, with a light step!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.57,0:13:24.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Quietly, like a feather.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.44,0:13:26.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, the girl you were with yesterday...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.44,0:13:29.03,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, one, two... One, two...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.03,0:13:29.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's leaving for Boston this evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.03,0:13:30.53,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, that's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.03,0:13:32.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's your friend, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.04,0:13:32.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.82,0:13:35.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, you're acting nervously around her.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.75,0:13:40.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, somehow, I can't act against Manami.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.38,0:13:41.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Sora Naegino!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.96,0:13:44.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think you're allowed \Nto speak during my class?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.96,0:13:44.97,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry. I'm sorry. I won't do it anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.97,0:13:47.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a big mistake if you think you \Ncan get away from being punished
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.51,0:13:49.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,just because you're playing a leading role!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.10,0:13:50.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.12,0:13:52.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Yuri.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.31,0:13:56.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me, sir; I would like \Nto invite Sora to lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.35,0:13:57.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,May I have your permission?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.15,0:13:57.92,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Yuri...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.92,0:13:58.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With Sora?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.77,0:14:02.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course. I will allow you anything you ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.91,0:14:05.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.94,0:14:08.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to have lunch with Mr. Yuri?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.16,0:14:16.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, shoot...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.25,0:14:18.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be so nervous.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.23,0:14:21.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well... I wish I could not be nervous.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.00,0:14:22.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.29,0:14:26.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one I've admired since \Neven before I joined Kaleido Stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.72,0:14:29.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm flattered.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.84,0:14:31.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, then,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.68,0:14:33.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you wouldn't mind joining me, would you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.56,0:14:36.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.68,0:14:39.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to come to my place
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.19,0:14:40.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,after you quit Kaleido Stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.90,0:14:44.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What... what did you just say?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.20,0:14:48.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to withdraw from \NKaleido Stage as of today.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.80,0:14:52.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to create a new troupe with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.74,0:14:54.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Yuri...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.24,0:14:58.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the new troupe, you, not \NLayla, will be the top star.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.04,0:15:01.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're... kidding, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.48,0:15:05.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You would never say that...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.18,0:15:07.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're kidding, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.59,0:15:10.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.55,0:15:14.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaleido Stage is not as \Ngreat a place as you think.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.35,0:15:17.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kalos has misled everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.76,0:15:20.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not asking you to make \Nup your mind right away,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.77,0:15:24.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I think it'll be to your own benefit \Nif you decide what you want to do fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.65,0:15:28.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're in trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.19,0:15:31.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After today, 25 people are \Ngoing to quit at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.82,0:15:34.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are we going to do starting tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.78,0:15:36.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have no choice but to \Nsuspend our performances.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.99,0:15:38.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess we have to...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.04,0:15:41.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I feel sorry for all \Nthose kids who are left here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.63,0:15:48.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I cannot believe this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.09,0:15:49.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even Mr. Yuri...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.30,0:15:52.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora, we're in trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.09,0:15:53.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.18,0:15:55.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Starting tomorrow, we \Nwon't be able to perform.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.55,0:15:59.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? We won't?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.35,0:16:01.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't believe this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.85,0:16:05.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After today's show, 25 \Npeople are going to quit.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.77,0:16:09.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even Mr. Yuri and the \Ndirectors are leaving...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.19,0:16:10.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.57,0:16:12.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.57,0:16:17.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm going to withdraw from \NKaleido Stage after today.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.45,0:16:21.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I want you to create a new troupe with me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.00,0:16:25.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Yuri really meant it when he said that...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.55,0:16:38.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I beat Kalos. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.82,0:16:59.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.23,0:17:02.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Today is the last. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.06,0:17:06.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Kaleido Stage... {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.42,0:17:11.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...will be gone?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.36,0:17:38.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry for what happened today.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.78,0:17:42.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's okay. The audience was happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.70,0:17:46.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuri tried to win you over, didn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.83,0:17:48.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.12,0:17:49.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.67,0:17:50.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.92,0:17:51.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.05,0:17:57.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems that someone offered to buy \Nout my father's stake in Kaleido Stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.51,0:18:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard he was a businessman in Las Vegas.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.72,0:18:05.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was aware that Yuri was up \Nto something for a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.48,0:18:11.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I was not able to change his mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.74,0:18:20.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess we have no chance to \Nuse this "Pirates" anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.99,0:18:22.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It could be...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.83,0:18:27.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Losing over 20 people changes everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.65,0:18:30.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.86,0:18:32.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have a nice evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.18,0:18:46.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for everything, for all this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.60,0:18:49.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you satisfied?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.32,0:18:50.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.35,0:18:53.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just being able to see you look \Nlike that really gratifies me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.25,0:19:08.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.17,0:19:12.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I saw your mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.92,0:19:14.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Manami...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.09,0:19:18.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry for showing you my goof.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.05,0:19:19.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.34,0:19:21.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I came here to apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.26,0:19:22.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.01,0:19:25.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I said something cruel yesterday,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.74,0:19:28.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,saying that I came here to \Nsee your regretful face.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.63,0:19:31.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I said that, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.85,0:19:33.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No. It's not like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.31,0:19:35.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't make a mistake because of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.86,0:19:39.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaleido Stage is in serious trouble now,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.47,0:19:42.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and we won't be able to perform for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.28,0:19:47.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After I was finally able to \Nco-star with Miss Layla too...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.29,0:19:49.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will Kaleido Stage be gone?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.62,0:19:51.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.00,0:19:55.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you still not regret coming here,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.36,0:19:58.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,even if Kaleido Stage disappears?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.56,0:20:01.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No. No regrets.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.17,0:20:02.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.34,0:20:05.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because it was my dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.66,0:20:11.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've always thought you were pretty dumb...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.48,0:20:12.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you really {\i1}are {\i0}dumb.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.65,0:20:16.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But... I envy you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.73,0:20:20.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to be a hairdresser.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.69,0:20:21.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.90,0:20:24.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I always got good grades.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.49,0:20:26.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So my parents expected me to \Ndo something more than that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.77,0:20:30.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The reason why I decided to study overseas \Nwas because it was getting stifling.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.33,0:20:32.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A hairstylist? That's nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.49,0:20:34.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I support you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.29,0:20:37.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why you're dumb.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.04,0:20:39.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Usually, things are not that simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.84,0:20:41.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... really?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.05,0:20:45.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't be like you, Sora.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.76,0:20:48.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I think I wanted to feel relieved
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.90,0:20:51.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,by looking at your regretful face.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.18,0:20:56.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not strong at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.81,0:21:00.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please cut my hair again.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.46,0:21:05.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm your first customer.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.52,0:21:08.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what kind of career you choose,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.01,0:21:10.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I support you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.70,0:21:15.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will try to do something \Nabout Kaleido Stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.00,0:21:16.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can keep worrying about it, \Nwondering if it'll just be gone,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.75,0:21:18.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but that won't change anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.58,0:21:21.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Instead, I should do something so \Nthat Kaleido Stage will not go away.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.58,0:21:22.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.34,0:21:26.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess even you can give serious \Nthought to things like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.97,0:21:28.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In my own way...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.94,0:21:34.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I need to be going.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.85,0:21:35.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.73,0:21:36.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, see you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.15,0:21:39.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, by the way,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.48,0:21:41.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,don't sleep without covering your stomach.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.64,0:21:42.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.36,0:22:01.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So what do you think about Mia's story, Boss?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.64,0:22:07.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it! He doesn't like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.94,0:22:09.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora, it's impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.22,0:22:12.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.81,0:22:14.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See? As I thought...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.60,0:22:17.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, Boss, if we use this story,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.06,0:22:20.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we may be able to put on a fun show \Neven though we don't have many people.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.44,0:22:21.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One week...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.68,0:22:25.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Make it so you can perform \Nthis on stage in one week.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.18,0:22:29.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.74,0:22:36.75,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Next Kaleido Star"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.46,0:22:40.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I might have gone beyond Shakespeare.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.25,0:22:44.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And so, Mia played a great active role \Nby directing the script she wrote.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.55,0:22:46.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}While Mr. Yuri's headhunting continues,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.67,0:22:49.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}the only thing we can do is do our best.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.43,0:22:51.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Miss Layla is against what we're doing,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.09,0:22:54.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}but I positively know Mia can pull it \Noff. I know she can! I know she can!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.96,0:22:56.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Next time on Kaleido Star, {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.97,0:22:57.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"Fire It Up! {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.77,0:22:59.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Amazing Mia."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.35,0:23:01.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My wings are my dream and \Non towards the sky...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.89,0:23:17.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm here between the sky and the \Nroads, and facing against the wind{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.54,0:23:32.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And I'm facing forward so the sorrow \Ndoesn't rain down ever again{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.47,0:23:38.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I came all the way here after \NI jumped over that wall{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.39,0:23:45.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There are many times when \NI just want to run away{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.65,0:23:51.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But I'm still here, so, \NI'm not daunted that much{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.07,0:23:58.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The poem I scribbled down, I can just \Nstart writing over from the beginning{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.45,0:24:04.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Unable to write it well, I'm laughing{\i0}
